<includeonly>{{Category/table | category={{{userparam|}}} | page={{{1|}}} | subobjects=no }}</includeonly><noinclude>
Renders a single subobject instance as a full Category/table.

Called from Category/subobjects via {{#ask: | format=template | template=Category/subobject-instance | userparam=<SubCat>}}:

* {{{1}}}       - the subobject's fragment identifier (e.g. "ParentPage#_abc123")
* {{{userparam}}} - the subobject's category name (without namespace prefix)

Reuses Category/table so subobjects render with the exact same look as
the parent category page. subobjects=no stops recursion into nested
subobjects.
</noinclude>
